transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thanks for calling Viagra, this is Charles.

Speaker 2: Yes, I got this prescription of Viagra and I didn't realize it was a subscription thing and I'm 79 years old and if you keep sending me some, I'm going to have more than I'm ever going to need in my whole life.

Speaker 1: Okay, alright, Dennis Cremings in Zimfree Hills, Florida?

Speaker 2: Yes.

Speaker 1: Alright, it does look like you are a VIP member here, so it's not so much of a subscription but a prescription that gets written up with refills, so understandably so Dennis, if you don't necessarily need the pills every single month, we can completely back off on sending them every single month.

Speaker 2: That's one of your perks of being a VIP member here.

Speaker 1: I can pause, freeze your account, we won't charge you or send you anything for the next five months, that way you have plenty of time to use what you've got.

Speaker 2: They won't come every single month after that, it'll be as needed, alright?

Speaker 1: Well, the other problem was it just came as regular Viagra and it wasn't the Viagra AGV.

Speaker 2: Is that right?

Speaker 1: Okay, so let me do this then Dennis, let me message my pharmacy, I will send you out replacements for free, I will message them myself right now and tell them to send you the Viagra AGV.

Speaker 2: The Viagra AGVs will have the number 100 pressed onto them like a stamp, okay, I guarantee you're going to love them and then I'll make sure that we continue that pause for the next couple of months, that way you have time to try them.

Speaker 1: Will they be white also?

Speaker 2: They will be white generic, excuse me, white diamond, excuse me, white diamond Pfizer's.

Speaker 1: Yeah, white diamond pills, that's Pfizer's signature trademark for Viagra and they will have the number 100, that's how you're able to identify them, okay?

Speaker 2: And the ones that I have, do you want them sent back or the ones that you're...

Speaker 1: If you want to keep them, if you want to keep them, keep them, all of our stuff is FDA approved, so try them out if you like them, great, if not, you have the AGVs on their way, okay?

Speaker 2: Okay, and if I get more than what I'm going to ever need, can it actually be canceled?

Speaker 1: Well, I'll pause everything, that way you have time to try it, I'll only send 10, I'll send the 20 that you originally ordered, and then after that, I'll pause it, so that nothing else comes and nothing else gets sent out to you, until you call us and let us know, okay?

Speaker 2: Okay, sounds good.

Speaker 1: Okay, sounds good, all right, Dennis, I'd expect them to arrive by hopefully Friday or Saturday, all right?

Speaker 2: Okay, thank you, appreciate it.

Speaker 1: Absolutely, absolutely, I hope you have a great one.

Speaker 2: Thanks, bye-bye.

Speaker 1: Bye-bye.
